{"tid":1216871,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"616一定要出 唔係白行","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:47:17.000Z","uid":136640,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"10ebaa4f3e8f71aa2aa74865fa40c63bbb3a2eb9","tid":1216871,"uid":136640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得遊行係白行 而唔出今次616<br />\n<br />\n遊行目的係制造輿論壓力，規模愈大，愈能表示市民對政府既不滿程度，仍引到其他國家對我地既關注<br />\n<br />\n上次103萬69遊行 香港政府當冇到 但已經成功吸引各國注意<br />\n<br />\n到612示威被武力清埋 更加多國家已經有發聲要求政府正視 特朗普都出埋聲（雖然係廢話）<br />\n<br />\n石禮謙因為認為社會動盪 而放棄111億既地皮<br />\n<br />\n依啲都係抗爭成功既證據<br />\n<br />\n政府都好想快速通過條例 但唔急於一時 拖我地兩三個星期 等我地戰意消退 再冇人反抗既時候 就只會話：政府經過多個星期既努力 說服曬市民<br />\n<br />\n所以各位 今次抗戰係持久戰 周日遊行係唯一可以令各位要返工返學既市民一同參與 表達自己訴求既行動 <br />\n<br />\n所以各位唔好放棄 我地唔係白行 一定要參與遊行 制造更多既輿論壓力比政府 <br />\n<br />\n（我個人意為政府依兩日都延遲開會 係有壓力影響緊 如果唔係今日咁少人 點解唔拿拿林開會過左佢？）"},{"pid":"18e24f6970ea1beb82b111249d6f99d62d6f992a","tid":1216871,"uid":214555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9780f8809deaf1d7f2ea1fdeff90c97a8cf241d2","tid":1216871,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05691036e18d27a3947ddc11fcc386566b8f9829","tid":1216871,"uid":219096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"是日最佳父親節活動"},{"pid":"8df991554b3cba3252a847dd0a5e43fb3b399cd9","tid":1216871,"uid":136640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"睇完唔好剩係like 幫手推埋上去比更加多人睇到"},{"pid":"397b8091a13a9e957eac0f6519adc4f26037da0f","tid":1216871,"uid":46091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd037aa67b4b6a5aabb91d9f0f4bece481a175f4","tid":1216871,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"講唔夠, call齊各路人馬, 民陣, 公會，學生會領就, 教會, 人力, 社民連, 帶備protect gear, 補給物資, GoPro, 尿袋, 來個聯合大反擊!"},{"pid":"43196eb6b43710981089ebb3390ca56ac31a9624","tid":1216871,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:45:40.000Z","msg":"得星期六一日call馬, 要夠快"},{"pid":"728d4d9bbfd3b41863f09262761c8bb52d111efa","tid":1216871,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"連續兩星期百萬人遊行，係史上從未見過，和理非既終極武器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216635/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216635/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a2244547bfee1bae925e6cb5dff575e8be2dc58d","tid":1216871,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"為自身安全, 記得帶暗cam，航拍都要"},{"pid":"19789aee0559a75a85c9d2a88bc15ac24cd3bef9","tid":1216871,"uid":136640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b53a9b340d44c5d020478b42d0b6dd34d951baea","tid":1216871,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">614 油油行動 正式啟動 </span><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊入黎發夢，幫手推同share出去<br />\n<br />\n614 油油行動 正式啟動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1217162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1217162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}